      <title>日本内阁批准刺激计划 以显示石破天惊取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/japan-s-ishiba-says-stimulus-overall-impact-to-be-250-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂的内阁批准了一项比去年规模略大的刺激计划，以履行其加大对难以应对成本上升的家庭和企业的支持的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/japan-s-ishiba-says-stimulus-overall-impact-to-be-250-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 01:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
